msgid "## 5 Online Service Deployment"
msgstr "## 5 在线服务部署"

msgid "### 5.1 Single-Node Online Deployment"
msgstr "### 5.1 单节点在线部署"

msgid ""
"PaddleOCR-VL supports single-node single-card deployment on the A2 series "
"and Atlas 300 inference products platform. Single-node deployment completes "
"both Prefill and Decode within the same node."
msgstr ""
"PaddleOCR-VL 支持在 A2 系列和 Atlas 300 推理产品平台上进行单节点单卡部署。单节点部署在同一节点内完成 Prefill 和 "
"Decode。"

msgid "Follow these steps to start the inference service:"
msgstr "按照以下步骤启动推理服务："

msgid ""
"1. Prepare model weights: Ensure the model weights are accessible. With `VLLM_USE_MODELSCOPE=True`, the model will be loaded automatically from ModelScope.\n"
"2. Set the `MODEL_PATH` environment variable to point to your model directory.\n"
"3. Create and execute the deployment script (save as `deploy.sh`)."
msgstr ""
"1. 准备模型权重：确保模型权重可访问。设置 `VLLM_USE_MODELSCOPE=True` 后，模型将从 ModelScope 自动加载。\n"
"2. 设置 `MODEL_PATH` 环境变量指向您的模型目录。\n"
"3. 创建并执行部署脚本（保存为 `deploy.sh`）。"

msgid "Startup Command:"
msgstr "启动命令："

msgid "On Atlas 300 inference products:"
msgstr "在 Atlas 300 推理产品上："

msgid ""
"- Only `float16` dtype is supported.\n"
"    - The `--max_model_len` option is added to prevent errors when generating the attention operator mask.\n"
"    - Graph compilation (`--compilation-config`) requires **CANN version >= 9.0.0**. If your CANN version is lower, please revert to eager mode by replacing the `--compilation-config` argument with `--enforce-eager`.\n"
"    - The `fuse_norm_quant` option in `--additional_config` is disabled (`false`) because it is not supported by the graph compilation on this hardware. Keep this setting unchanged."
msgstr ""
"- 仅支持 `float16` 数据类型。\n"
"    - 添加了 `--max_model_len` 选项以防止生成注意力算子掩码时出错。\n"
"    - 图编译（`--compilation-config`）需要 **CANN 版本 >= 9.0.0**。如果您的 CANN 版本较低，请通过将 `--compilation-config` 参数替换为 `--enforce-eager` 来恢复到 eager 模式。\n"
"    - `--additional_config` 中的 `fuse_norm_quant` 选项被禁用（`false`），因为此硬件上的图编译不支持该选项。请保持此设置不变。"

msgid "Key Parameter Descriptions:"
msgstr "关键参数说明："

msgid ""
"- `--max-num-batched-tokens` specifies the maximum number of tokens batched in a single forward pass. Adjust this parameter for throughput optimization.\n"
"- `--max_model_len` specifies the maximum context length — that is, the sum of input and output tokens for a single request.\n"
"- `--no-enable-prefix-caching` indicates that prefix caching is disabled. To enable it, remove this option.\n"
"- `--mm-processor-cache-gb` sets the size of the multimodal processor cache (in GB). A value of `0` disables caching.\n"
"- `--dtype float16` specifies the model dtype. On Atlas 300 inference products, only `float16` is supported.\n"
"- `--compilation-config '{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` enables full decode graph compilation for improved performance. On Atlas 300 inference products, `fuse_norm_quant` in graph compilation is disabled by default in `--additional_config`.\n"
"- `--additional_config '{\"enable_cpu_binding\":true}'` enables CPU binding to improve performance."
msgstr ""
"- `--max-num-batched-tokens` 指定单次前向传播中批处理的最大 token 数量。调整此参数以优化吞吐量。\n"
"- `--max_model_len` 指定最大上下文长度——即单个请求的输入和输出 token 之和。\n"
"- `--no-enable-prefix-caching` 表示禁用前缀缓存。要启用它，请移除此选项。\n"
"- `--mm-processor-cache-gb` 设置多模态处理器缓存的大小（以 GB 为单位）。值为 `0` 表示禁用缓存。\n"
"- `--dtype float16` 指定模型数据类型。在 Atlas 300 推理产品上，仅支持 `float16`。\n"
"- `--compilation-config '{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` 启用完整解码图编译以提高性能。在 Atlas 300 推理产品上，`--additional_config` 中默认禁用了图编译的 `fuse_norm_quant`。\n"
"- `--additional_config '{\"enable_cpu_binding\":true}'` 启用 CPU 绑定以提高性能。"

