msgid "## 9 Performance Tuning"
msgstr "## 9 性能调优"

msgid "### 9.1 Recommended Configurations"
msgstr "### 9.1 推荐配置"

msgid ""
"> **Note**: The following configurations are validated in specific test "
"environments and are for reference only. The optimal configuration depends "
"on factors such as maximum input/output length, precision requirements, and "
"actual hardware specifications. It is recommended to refer to Section 9.2 "
"for tuning based on actual conditions."
msgstr ""
"> **注意**：以下配置在特定测试环境中验证，仅供参考。最佳配置取决于最大输入/输出长度、精度要求和实际硬件规格等因素。建议参考第 9.2 "
"节根据实际情况进行调优。"

msgid ""
"PaddleOCR-VL is a lightweight model that runs on a single NPU. The key "
"tuning parameters differ between hardware platforms."
msgstr "PaddleOCR-VL 是一个轻量级模型，运行在单个 NPU 上。关键调优参数因硬件平台而异。"

msgid "#### Table 1: Scenario Overview"
msgstr "#### 表 1：场景概览"

msgid ""
"| Scenario | Hardware | *Total NPUs | Weight Version | Key Considerations |\n"
"|----------|----------|------------|---------------|-------------------|\n"
"| High Throughput | A2 series | 1 | PaddleOCR-VL-0.9B | - |\n"
"| High Throughput | Atlas 300 inference products | 1 | PaddleOCR-VL-0.9B | Graph compilation requires **CANN >= 9.0.0** |"
msgstr ""
"| 场景 | 硬件 | *NPU 总数 | 权重版本 | 关键考虑因素 |\n"
"|----------|----------|------------|---------------|-------------------|\n"
"| 高吞吐 | A2 系列 | 1 | PaddleOCR-VL-0.9B | - |\n"
"| 高吞吐 | Atlas 300 推理产品 | 1 | PaddleOCR-VL-0.9B | 图编译需要 **CANN >= 9.0.0** |"

msgid ""
"> `*Total NPUs` indicates the total number of NPUs used across all nodes."
msgstr "> `*NPU 总数` 表示所有节点使用的 NPU 总数。"

msgid "#### Table 2: Detailed Node Configuration"
msgstr "#### 表 2：详细节点配置"

msgid ""
"| Scenario | Configuration | NPUs | TP | DP | Max Model Len | Max Num Batched Tokens | Graph Compilation | dtype |\n"
"|----------|-------------|------|----|----|---------------|------------------------|--------------------|-------|\n"
"| High Throughput | A2 series / Single Machine | 1 | — | — | — | 16384 | FULL_DECODE_ONLY | bfloat16 (default) |\n"
"| High Throughput | Atlas 300 inference products / Single Machine | 1 | — | — | 16384 | — | FULL_DECODE_ONLY; otherwise enforce-eager | float16 |"
msgstr ""
"| 场景 | 配置 | NPU 数量 | TP | DP | 最大模型长度 | 最大批处理 Token 数 | 图编译 | dtype |\n"
"|----------|-------------|------|----|----|---------------|------------------------|--------------------|-------|\n"
"| 高吞吐 | A2 系列 / 单机 | 1 | — | — | — | 16384 | FULL_DECODE_ONLY | bfloat16 (默认) |\n"
"| 高吞吐 | Atlas 300 推理产品 / 单机 | 1 | — | — | 16384 | — | FULL_DECODE_ONLY；否则使用 enforce-eager | float16 |"

msgid ""
"> For complete startup commands and parameter descriptions, please refer to "
"the deployment examples in [Section 5.1](#51-single-node-online-deployment)."
msgstr ""
"> 完整的启动命令和参数说明，请参考 [第 5.1 节](#51-single-node-online-deployment) 中的部署示例。"

