msgid ""
"- **Q: What are the deployment requirements for Atlas 300 inference "
"products?**"
msgstr "- **问：Atlas 300 推理产品的部署要求是什么？**"

msgid ""
"A: On Atlas 300 inference products, only `float16` dtype is supported. Graph"
" compilation (`--compilation-config`) requires **CANN version >= 9.0.0**; if"
" your CANN version is lower, use `--enforce-eager` instead."
msgstr ""
"答：在 Atlas 300 推理产品上，仅支持 `float16` 数据类型。图编译 (`--compilation-config`) 需要 "
"**CANN 版本 >= 9.0.0**；如果您的 CANN 版本较低，请改用 `--enforce-eager`。"

msgid ""
"- **Q: What should I do if I encounter dependency conflicts during "
"installation on Atlas 300 inference products?**"
msgstr "- **问：在 Atlas 300 推理产品上安装时遇到依赖冲突怎么办？**"

msgid ""
"A: You may need to uninstall `triton-ascend` to avoid dependency conflicts. "
"See [Section 4.2](#42-source-code-installation) for details."
msgstr ""
"答：您可能需要卸载 `triton-ascend` 以避免依赖冲突。详见[第 4.2 节](#42-source-code-installation)。"
